source.name: CIBExpensesFY11
source.description: Provides expenditure data summarized by each agency and general ledger (GL) account. The general ledger account may be viewed by major class, sub-class or detail expenditure code.  Examples of the major class expenditure category include: Personal Services; Travel Expenses; Administrative Expense; Property, Furniture, Equipment and Related Debt; General Assistance, Awards, Grants, & Other; Program-Directed Payments ; and Transfers and Other Disbursements.
